name: Chill Cowboy Danielle Bradbery Tooele UT Tickets

metadata.name: Danielle Bradbery Concert Tickets @ Tooele, UT
metadata.description:
This product will serve as 2 tickets and 2 meet and greets to Danielle Bradbery in Tooele, Utah on July 28th at 4:30  pm. 

 
Further details will be communicated via Bunches App. Please download Bunches from the apps store and login with your wallet in order to join the DB Utah concert group chat. Other Cowboy Tix holders will be able to communicate in this space for day of show gathering along with admin who can help during day of show directions and perks for holders. You are allowed to buy, sell, or trade these tickets. New holders must notify admin prior to 10am day of show of any transactions via bunches. These tickets can be sold to anyone with a crypto wallet. This NFT serves as your access to community, directions, and a relic of the show you attended.
